===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# {{lb|en|linguistics}} The study of the physical [[sounds]] of human [[speech]], concerned with the physical properties of speech sounds (phones), and the processes of their physiological production, auditory reception, and neurophysiological perception, and their representation by written symbols.

